General.Name: Advanced Packaging Tech (Malaysia)
General.Description: Advanced Packaging Technology (M) Bhd manufactures and distributes flexible packaging materials primarily in Malaysia, Mauritius, and Brunei. It offers single and multi-layers flexible packaging materials in roll and pouch/bag forms. The company also provides management services. It markets its products to various industries, including snack foods, instant noodles, sweets and confectionery, liquid condiments, frozen foods, spices, beverages, milk powder, edible oil, rice, medical/surgical products and pharmaceuticals, and others. The company was incorporated in 1982 and is headquartered in Bandar Baru Bangi, Malaysia.
